{"article_id":"n7Vf7EtkUwjQvbvu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A U.S. judge fiercely criticized President Donald Trump ' s former national security adviser Michael Flynn on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"for lying to FBI agents in a probe into Russian interference in the 2016 election ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and delayed sentencing him","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"until Flynn has finished helping prosecutors .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"U.S. District Judge Emmet Sullivan told Flynn , a retired U.S. Army lieutenant general and former director of the Defense Intelligence Agency ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that he had arguably betrayed his country .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Sullivan also noted","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that Flynn had operated as an undeclared lobbyist for Turkey","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"even as he worked on Trump ' s campaign team","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and prepared to be his White House national security adviser .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Flynn pleaded guilty to lying to FBI agents about his December 2016 conversations with Sergei Kislyak , then Russia ' s ambassador in Washington , about U.S. sanctions","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"imposed on Moscow by the administration of Trump ' s Democratic predecessor Barack Obama .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"The conversations took place between Trump ' s November election victory and his inauguration in January 2017 .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Special Counsel Robert Mueller ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"leading the investigation into possible collusion between Trump ' s campaign and Russia ahead of the election ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"had asked the judge not to sentence Flynn to prison","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"because he had already provided \" substantial \" cooperation over the course of many interviews .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Lying to the FBI carries a statutory maximum sentence of five years in prison .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Flynn ' s plea agreement stated","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"that he was eligible for a sentence of between zero and six months .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Sullivan sternly told Flynn","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"his actions were abhorrent ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"noting","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"that Flynn had also lied to senior White House officials ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"who in turn misled the public .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The judge said","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"he had read additional facts about Flynn ' s behavior","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that have not been made public .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"At one point , Sullivan asked prosecutors","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"if Flynn could have been charged with treason ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"although the judge later said","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"he had not been suggesting","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"such a charge was warranted .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"\" Arguably , you sold your country out , \"","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"Sullivan told Flynn .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" I ' m not hiding my disgust , my disdain for this criminal offense . \"","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Related Coverage","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"Factbox :","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Mueller and other probes","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"posing risk for Trump","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Flynn ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"dressed in a suit and tie ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"showed little emotion throughout the hearing ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"and spoke calmly","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"when he confirmed his guilty plea","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"and answered questions from the judge .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Sullivan appeared ready to sentence Flynn to prison","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"but then gave him the option of a delay in his sentencing","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"so he could fully cooperate with any pending investigations","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"and bolster his case for leniency .","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"The judge told Flynn","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"he could not promise","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"that he would not eventually sentence him to serve prison time .","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"Flynn accepted that offer .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"Sullivan did not set a new date for sentencing","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"but asked Mueller ' s team and Flynn ' s attorney to give him a status report by March 13 .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Sullivan later imposed travel restrictions on Flynn ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"ordering him to surrender his passport and to obtain court permission","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"before traveling outside the Washington area .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"The curbs are typical for people","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"released on their own recognizance ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"the judge said .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Prosecutors said","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Flynn already had provided most of the cooperation","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"he could ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"but it was possible he might be able to help investigators further .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Flynn ' s attorney said","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"his client is cooperating with federal prosecutors in a case against Bijan Rafiekian , his former business partner","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"who has been charged with unregistered lobbying for Turkey .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Rafiekian pleaded not guilty on Tuesday to those charges in federal court in Alexandria , Virginia .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"His trial is scheduled for Feb. 11 .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Flynn is expected to testify .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Prosecutors have said","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Rafiekian and Flynn lobbied to have Washington extradite a Muslim cleric","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"who lives in the United States","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and is accused by Turkey ' s government of backing a 2016 coup attempt .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"Flynn has not been charged in that case .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Former U.S. national security adviser Michael Flynn departs","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"after his sentencing was delayed at U.S. District Court in Washington , U.S. , December 18 , 2018 .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"/Joshua Roberts","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Flynn was a high-profile adviser to Trump ' s campaign team .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"At the Republican Party ' s national convention in 2016 , Flynn led Trump ' s supporters in cries of \" Lock her up ! \"","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"directed against Democratic candidate Hillary Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"A group of protesters ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"including some","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"who chanted \" Lock him up , \"","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"gathered outside the courthouse on Tuesday , along with a large inflatable rat","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"fashioned","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"to look like Trump .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Several Flynn supporters also were there ,","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"cheering","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"as he entered","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and exited .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"One held a sign","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"that read ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"\" Michael Flynn is a hero . \"","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Flynn became national security adviser","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"when Trump took office in January 2017 ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"but lasted only 24 days","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"before being fired .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"He told FBI investigators on Jan. 24 , 2017 ,","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"that he had not discussed the U.S. sanctions with Kislyak","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"when in fact he had ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"according to his plea agreement .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Trump has said","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"he fired Flynn","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"because he also lied to Vice President Mike Pence about the contacts with Kislyak .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Trump has said","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Flynn did not break the law","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"and has voiced support for him ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"raising speculation","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"the Republican president might pardon him .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"\" Good luck today in court to General Michael Flynn .","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"Will be interesting to see what he has to say ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"despite tremendous pressure","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"being put on him ,","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"about Russian Collusion in our great and , obviously , highly successful political campaign .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"There was no Collusion ! \"","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"Trump wrote on Twitter on Tuesday morning .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"After the hearing , White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders told reporters","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"the FBI had \" ambushed \" Flynn in the way","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"agents questioned him ,","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"but said","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"his \" activities \" at the center of the case \" don ' t have anything to do with the president \"","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"and disputed","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"that Flynn had committed treason .","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"In contrast , Trump has called his former long-time personal lawyer Michael Cohen ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"who has pleaded guilty to separate charges ,","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"a \" rat . \"","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Mueller ' s investigation into Russia ' s role in the 2016 election and whether Trump has unlawfully sought to obstruct the probe has cast a shadow over his presidency .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Several former Trump aides have pleaded guilty in Mueller ' s probe ,","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"but Flynn was the first former Trump White House official","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"to do so .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"Mueller also has charged a series of Russian individuals and entities .","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"Trump has called Mueller ' s investigation a \" witch hunt \"","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"and has denied collusion with Moscow .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"Russia has denied meddling in the election , contrary to the conclusion of U.S. intelligence agencies","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"that have said","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Moscow used hacking and propaganda","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"to try to sow discord in the United States","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"and boost Trump ' s chances against Clinton .","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":283,"left":0,"right":282,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":282,"left":177,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":151,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":145,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":143,"right":144,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":146,"right":149,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":7,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":8,"right":147,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":176,"left":160,"right":175,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":160,"left":153,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":13,"relation